# 🦖 Dino Game (Pygame Edition)

A polished recreation of the classic Chrome Dino game built using Python and Pygame.

This project demonstrates core game development concepts including:

- Game loops
- Object-oriented programming
- Collision detection
- Sprite animation systems
- Jump physics
- Dynamic obstacle spawning
- Day/Night visual transitions

The goal of this project was not only to recreate the original Chrome Dino experience, but also to build a clean and extensible game architecture using Python.

---

