# ✨ Features

## 🎮 Gameplay

- Smooth dinosaur movement
- Physics-based jumping system
- Endless runner gameplay

## 🚧 Obstacles

- Random cactus spawning
- Flying bird enemies
- Dynamic obstacle timing

## 🌗 Visual Effects

- Day/Night cycle
- Smooth background transitions
- Animated sprites

## 🔊 Audio

- Jump sound effects
- Death sound effects
- Score point sound effects

## 🏆 Score System

- Real-time score tracking
- Local high score saving
- Persistent score storage

